---
title: Enterprise Conversational Customer Experience Platform | NHANCE NOW
"description": "Simplifying the way consumers connect, interact and transact with your brand with personalized conversational experiences, across digital channels."
---
extends layouts/_layout
block content
  block header
    include partials/_header
  .midmarket
    .intro
      .container.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1s")
        strong Conversational Solutions For Mid Market Business
        h2 Be the business today's customers love
        p Shed your traditional avatar with a millennial friendly conversational makeover to your brand experiences. Personalize and deepen your customer relationships to accelerate growth at scale.
        a(href="#schedule" rel="modal:open") Request a Demo
    .midmarket__curated
      .container
        h2 Curated solutions to become a conversational business
        .midmarket__curated__row
          .midmarket__curated__block.midmarket__curated__block--1.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .midmarket__curated__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/hub.png", alt="")
            h4 Conversational Experience Hub
            p Provide your customers with a single place to manage all post-purchase experiences through personalized conversations.
            a(href="use-cases.html") See Use Cases
          .midmarket__curated__block.midmarket__curated__block--2.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .midmarket__curated__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/commerce.png", alt="")
            h4 Conversational Commerce
            p Advise and assist your customers in realtime to personalize, simplify and quicken their purchase decisions.
            a(href="use-cases.html") See Use Cases
          .midmarket__curated__block.midmarket__curated__block--3.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .midmarket__curated__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/support.png", alt="")
            h4 Conversational Support
            p Make it easy for your customers to get responses to queries and access to information, 24/7, through instant conversations.
            a(href="use-cases.html") See Use Cases
    .midmarket__features
      .container
        .row.no-gutters.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/midmarket-graphic-01.png", alt="")
          .col-lg-5.col-md-6.col-12.offset-lg-1.order-first
            .features-scroller__text.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h3 Give your customers experiences that matches their lifestyle
              p In today's conversational era your customers no longer prefer to visit websites, write emails or call helplines to talk to your brand. They prefer seamless and casual conversations, smart apps, natural voice services to get their things done.
              p NHANCE NOW tools help you shed outdated CX avatars and give your brand experience a fresh outlook that is more in sync with the digitally empowered lifestyle that your customers are used too.
        .row.no-gutters.features-scroller__row
          .col-lg-5.col-md-6.col-12
            .features-scroller__text.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h3 The ultimate unified customer experience
              p In order to offer more services and make your customer's life easier you offer more interation touch points which actually makes it harder for them to interact with your business.
              p Using our conversational gateways or DX Cards you can bring together all these brand touch points and service offering onto a single place for your customers. Create unified experience hubs, that help your customers find whatever they need and for you to deliver all services over a single touch point.
          .col-lg-7.col-md-6.col-12.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/midmarket-graphic-02.png", alt="")
        .row.no-gutters.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/midmarket-graphic-03.png", alt="")
          .col-md-6.col-12.order-first
            .features-scroller__text.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h3 The fastest and easiest way to talk to you
              p Millennials are perpetually time strapped. They are always on the lookout for the fastest channel to get what they need and the most convenient way to get it done. They expect every business to respect their sense of urgency and ease. Using our Bots, instant messaging channels and our app and mobile friendly DX Cards you can enable your customers to easily start real time conversations in times of need, skip the queue to access important information and complete transactions in the blink of an eye.
        .row.no-gutters.features-scroller__row
          .col-lg-5.col-md-6.col-12
            .features-scroller__text.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h3 Build a personal relationship with each customer
              p When you talk to your customers just the way their friends would, you build deeper relationships with them and earn a bigger share of their trust. Our conversational tools enable you to have this deep level of personalization with customers on their most private channels, with contextually rich interactions. Craft personalized DX Cards or have friendly conversations over WhatsApp, Messenger and Alexa devices to support, guide and transact and earn meaningful loyalty.
          .col-lg-7.col-md-6.col-12.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/midmarket-graphic-04.png", alt="")
    .customer-success
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-5.col-12
          .col-md-7.col-12
            .customer-success__text.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h3 Customer proof
              p "The key to increasing our life time revenue from our customers was having realtime conversations with them to help with instant answers to product related queries, smart recommendations and purchase fulfilment."
              strong Mohd. Waseem
              span Chief - Customer Success, AE Tickets
              //- img(src="img/midmarket/iticket.png", alt="")
    .midmarket__features
      .container
        .row.no-gutters.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img
              img(src="img/midmarket/tools.png", alt="")
          .col-lg-5.col-md-6.col-12.offset-lg-1.order-first
            .features-scroller__text.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h3 Come along with all your favourite tools
              p We want you to leverage our platform with minimal changes to the way you work, hence we have made it easy to blend with your existing IT systems.
              p NHANCE NOW integrates smoothly and securely with all your business applications. Sync data, import and export content effortlessly between systems to simplify and improve every experience interaction.
    .midmarket__security
      .container
        h2 Get best in class security & compliance
        .row
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6.col-12
            .midmarket__security__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h4 Hosting
              p Application and data hosted on Amazon Web Services, world's foremost cloud hosting service.
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6.col-12
            .midmarket__security__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h4 Encryption
              p All data transmission encrypted with AES, 128-bit key length.
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6.col-12
            .midmarket__security__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h4 Operational
              p Compliant with geography based data laws, network security protocols, data storage and redundancy, vulnerability scanning and patching.
          .col-xl-3.col-lg-6.col-12
            .midmarket__security__block.wow.flipInY(data-wow-duration="1s")
              h4 Authentication
              p 2 Factor Authentication, User Roles and Permissions.


    .midmarket__follow
      .container
        h2 We stay with you every step of the way
        .midmarket__follow__row
          .midmarket__follow__block.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
            img(src="img/midmarket/team.png", alt="")
            h4 Team walkthroughs
            p Once you onboard with us, we will take your team through account setup, configurations, live demos and business use cases.
          .midmarket__follow__block.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
            img(src="img/midmarket/dedicated.png", alt="")
            h4 Dedicated support
            p Get a single point of contact and priority support channel access for seamless and uninterrupted support.
          .midmarket__follow__block.wow.zoomIn(data-wow-duration="1s")
            img(src="img/midmarket/knowledge-hub.png", alt="")
            h4 Knowledge hub
            p Free Access to blogs, whitepapers, webinars to receive tactical advise, understand trends to craft winning conversational strategies.
        .message__channels-other__btn
          strong Let's get you started
          p Our friendly executives are waiting to help you get going
          a(href="#schedule" rel="modal:open") Setup Your Custom Demo
            span 100% Free to get started
  block footer
    include partials/_footer